quran[112]{c,v,t}:
  21,1,"ЖҒadanike yimЙ“e Й“en hasboore maЙ“Й“e nden, te kamЙ“e hiЙ“e e nder welsindaare ko Й“e Й—urniiЙ“e"
  21,2,Arataa e maЙ“Й“e waaju immorde ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e ko fuЙ—Й—aa si wanaa Й“e jentike nde hara kamЙ“e hiЙ“e fija
  21,3,"ЖҒerЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en ko welsandiiЙ—e Й“en tooГұuЙ“e suuЙ—a cowndi(gunndo) [wi'a] enee, hara oo wonu si wanaa Й“anndinke yeru mo'on, kaa on aray e mbilewu hara onon hiЙ—on sutii (ndaara)"
  21,4,"O maaki: \"Joomi am no Anndi Konngol ngol ka kammu e ka Leydi Kanko ko O Nanoowo AnnduЙ—o On"
  21,5,"Ko woni, Й“e wi'u: \"Ko nde jiiЙ“u-jaaЙ“u koyЙ—i, toode, o fefindi nde, ko woni, kanko ko o yimoowo, awa yo o addan en Aayewal wano aranЙ“e Й“en Nuliranoo non"
  21,6,"GomЙ—inaali ado maЙ“Й“e immorde e saare Men halki nde. Enee, hara ko kamЙ“e goomЙ—ita"
  21,7,"Men Nulaali ado maaЙ—a si wanaa worЙ“e Men Wahayina e maЙ“Й“e, lanndee yimЙ“e defte Й“en si tawii wonii on anndaa. @Corrected"
  21,8,"Men waЙ—aali Й“e Й“alli Й“e Гұaamataa Гұaametee, Й“e laataaki kadi luttinteeЙ“e"
  21,9,"Refti Men Goonginani Й“e Fodoore nden Men danndi Й“e wonndude e Й“en Й“e Men Muuyi, Men halki fantinЙ“e Й“en"
  21,10,GomЙ—ii Men jippinii faade e mooЙ—on Deftere no e nder mayre jaЕӢtawol mooЙ—on. Kaa on hakkiltaa
  21,11,Heewii ko Men halki immorde e saare laatinoonde ko tooГұunde Men fuЙ—Й—i Й“aawo mayre yimЙ“e goo
  21,12,"Tuma nde Й“e so'unoo Lepte Amen Й—en, tawi kamЙ“e hiЙ“e doga Й—e"
  21,13,"Wata on dogu, ruttee faade e ko neeminaЙ—on kon e mu'un e koЙ—anЙ—e mo'on, belajo'o on lannditoyte"
  21,14,"ЖҒe wi'a: \"Eeyoo, bone amen, pellet, menen men laatinoke tooГұuЙ“e\". @Corrected"
  21,15,"Seerataa ndun noddaandu maЙ“Й“e, haa Men waЙ—a Й“e coГұateeri ko Й“e mayЙ“e"
  21,16,Men tagaali kammu ngun e leydi ndin e ko woni kon hakkunde majji ko Men fijooЙ“e
  21,17,"Sinndo Men faandino nde Men jogotoo fijindaaru, Men jogitotono Й—um immorde ka Amen si tawii Men laatike waЙ—ooЙ“e"
  21,18,"Ko woni, MeЙ—en werloo Goonga kan e dow meere nden ka munca nde, tawa kayre ko nde fuuyoore, no woodani on bone kon ko sifotoЙ—on"
  21,19,"Ko Kanko woodani ko woni kon ka kammuuli e ka leydi Й“en wonuЙ“e ka Makko kadi Й“e mawnittaako gaayi rewugol Mo, Й“e hasrintaaka kadi"
  21,20,HiЙ“e Subhinoo jemma e Гұalorma Й“e aamataa
  21,21,"Kaa Й“e jogiti reweteeЙ—i ka leydi hara kannji hiЙ—i immintina [mayЙ“e Й“en]"
  21,22,"Sinndo laatino e majji [kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin] rewteeЙ—i ko wonaa Alla Й—i bonayno. Senayee wonanii Alla Jom Arsi kin gaayi koЙ“e sifotoo. @Corrected"
  21,23,"O lanndetaake ko O gollata kon, kamЙ“e ko Й“e lannditoyteeЙ“e"
  21,24,"Kaa Й“e jogiti gaanin Makko reweteeЙ—i? Maaki: \"Addee daliili mon on, ko ndee woni jaЕӢta Й“en wonnduЙ“e e am e jaЕӢta Й“en adiiЙ“e lam\". Ko woni, Й“urЙ“e Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e Й“e anndaa Goonga kan kamЙ“e ko Й“e Й—urniiЙ“e"
  21,25,"Men Nulaali ado maaЙ—a immorde e NulaaЙ—o si wanaa Men wahayinii e makko; pellet, reweteeЙ—o alaa si wanaa Min Rewee Lam"
  21,26,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Hinnorante On jogitike Й“iЙ—Й—o\". Senayee woodanii Mo, ko woni, [Й“en ko Й“e] jeyaaЙ“e teddinaaЙ“e"
  21,27,"ЖҒe adortaa Mo konngol ngol, kamЙ“e ko Yamiroore Makko nden Й“e gollata"
  21,28,"Himo Anndi ko woni kon hedde yeeso maЙ“Й“e e ko woni kon hedde Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e, Й“e tefanoytaa si wanaa on mo O Weltanii, kamЙ“e immorde e kulol Makko ko Й“e jootuЙ“e"
  21,29,"Kala e maЙ“Й“e kadi wi'uЙ—o: \"Min ko mi reweteeЙ—o gaanin Makko\". On Й—on Men YoЙ“ay mo Jahanna- ma ko wano nii Men YoЙ“irta tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  21,30,"Enee, hara Й“en yedduЙ“e yi'aali wonndema kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin Й—i laatinoke hippondirЙ—i, Men Udditi Й—i Men waЙ—i immorde e ndiyam Й—am kala huunde wuuru nde. Kaa Й“e gomЙ—intaa"
  21,31,"Men waЙ—i ka leydi pelle fii wata nde ooГұodo e maЙ“Й“e, Men waЙ—i e mayri Й—ate yaajuЙ—e, belajo'o kamЙ“e Й“e feeway"
  21,32,"Men waЙ—i kammu ngun kippudi reenaandi, kamЙ“e ko Й“e Й—urniiЙ“e gaayi Aayeeje Amen Й—en"
  21,33,Ko Kanko woni On TaguЙ—o jemma on e Гұalorma on e naange ngen e lewru ndun kala majji hiЙ—i fubboo(lummboo) ka fuluku
  21,34,"Men waЙ—anaali Й“anndunke ado maaЙ—a luttineede, enee, hara si a maayii ko kamЙ“e woni luttinteeЙ“e Й“en"
  21,35,"Kala wonkii meedat mayЙ—e nden, Men jarribora on bone on e moЖҙЖҙere nden jarrabagol, ko ka Amen kadi ruttotoЙ—on"
  21,36,"Si Й“en yedduЙ“e yi'ii ma, Й“e jogitortaa ma si wanaa jalkitde [Й“e wiвҖҷa:] \"Enee, hara ko oo woni on jaЕӢtotooЙ—o reweteeЙ—i mo'on Й—in?\" hara kamЙ“e ko Й“e yedduЙ“e jantagol Hinnorante On"
  21,37,"NeЙ—Й—ake on Tagaama immorde e hawjere, aray Mi holla on Aayeeje Am Й—en wata on hawju"
  21,38,"HiЙ“e wi'a: \"Ko honnde tuma woni ndee Fodoore, si tawii ko on goonguЙ“e"
  21,39,"Sinndo Й“en yedduЙ“e anndiino tuma tawi Й“e ittataa Yiite ngen ka geece maЙ“Й“e wanaa kadi ka Й“abbe maЙ“Й“e kadi, kamЙ“e Й“e wonaali walloyteeЙ“e"
  21,40,"Ko woni, nge aray e maЙ“Й“e e juhayee nge muga Й“e, hara Й“e hattantaake ruttugol nge, Й“e wonaali kadi nennanoyteeЙ“e"
  21,41,"GomЙ—ii NulaaЙ“e goo jalkitanooma ado maaЙ—a, jippii e Й“en jalkituЙ“e ko Й“e laatinoo hiЙ“e jalkita"
  21,42,"Maaku: \"Ko hommbo reenata on jemma e Гұalorma immorde e Hinnorante On, ko woni, kamЙ“e gaayi jaЕӢta Joomi maЙ“Й“e ko Й“e Й—urniiЙ“e"
  21,43,"Kaa no woodani Й“e reeweteeЙ“e Й“e no dannda Й“e gaanin Amen? ЖҒe hattantaake wallude hay wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e, wanaa kamЙ“e woni wondateeЙ“e immorde e Amen"
  21,44,"Ko woni, Men dakmitii Й“ee e baabiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en haa ngurndam Й—am juutani Й“e. Enee, hara Й“ee yi'aali wonnde Menen MeЙ—en ara e leydi ndin Men ustira ndi immorde e seraaji mayri? Kaa ko kamЙ“e woni foolooЙ“e Й“en"
  21,45,"Maaku: \"Anndu ko mi woni jertinirde on ko Wahyu on, [kono] paho on nanataa noddaandu ndun, si Й“e jertinaama"
  21,46,"Mi woondii si meemii Й“e seeЙ—a immorde e Lepte Joomi maa Й—en, maa Й“e wi'a: \"Ee-yoo, bone amen pellet, menen men laatinoke tooГұuЙ“e"
  21,47,"Men waЙ—a manndikirЙ—e(peesirЙ—e) NunЙ—al ngal fii Г‘alnde Darngal hara wonkii woo toГұiroytaake hay e huunde, hay si laatii ko yeru gabbun pamarun Men adday kun Men yonii HasbooЙ“e"
  21,48,GomЙ—ii Men Okkii Muusaa e Haaruuna Serndoore nden e ndayngu e jaЕӢta wonannde hulooЙ“e Й“en
  21,49,ЖҒen hulayЙ“e Joomi maЙ“Й“e ka wirnii hara kamЙ“e immorde e Darngal ngal ko Й“e huli
  21,50,"Ndee [AlqurвҖҷaanaare] ko nde JaЕӢta, ko nde barkinaande Men Jippiniinde. Kaa onon ko on yeddayЙ“e nde"
  21,51,"GomЙ—ii Men Okkii Ibraahiima Peewal makko ngal ko adii, Men laatike kadi AnnduЙ“e mo"
  21,52,"Tuma nde o maakannoo baaba makko e yimЙ“e makko Й“en: \"Ko honЙ—um woni Й—ii nanndonlaaji nate mahiiЙ—e, Й—in Й—i ufiniЙ—on e [dewal] mu'un"
  21,53,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Men taw baabiraaЙ“e amen Й“en no rewde Й—i"
  21,54,"O maaki: \"GomЙ—ii on laatike onon e baabiraaЙ“e mon Й“en e nder majjere Й“anngunde wonЙ—on"
  21,55,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Enee, ko Goonga kan addanЙ—aa men, kaa an ko e fijooЙ“e Й“en jeyaЙ—aa"
  21,56,"Maaku: \"Ko woni, Joomi mo'on ko Jooma kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin On TaguЙ—oЙ—i, min komi jeyaaЙ—o e seediiЙ“e Й“en e dow Й—um"
  21,57,"Mi woondirii Alla, maa mi fewja fii Й—ii sanamuuji mo'on Й“aawo huccitugol mo'on ko on ruЕӢii Й“e"
  21,58,"O waЙ—i Й—i kunte, si wanaa mawndu majji ndun, belajo'o kamЙ“e Й“e ruttoto e mayru"
  21,59,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Ko hommbo waЙ—i Й—u'un e reweteeЙ—i amen Й—in? Pellet, on ko o jeyaaЙ—o e tooГұuЙ“e Й“en"
  21,60,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Men naniino suka no jaЕӢtoo Й—i ko Ibraahiima o wi'etaa"
  21,61,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Addee mo yeeso gite yimЙ“e Й“en, belajo'o Й“e seedoto"
  21,62,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Enee, Ibraahiima ko an waЙ—i Й—u'um Й—oo e reweteeЙ—i amen Й—in"
  21,63,"O maaki: \"Ko woni, ko mawndu majji ndun golle Й—um, lanndeeЙ—i si tawii Й—i laatike hiЙ—i wowla"
  21,64,"ЖҒe ruttii faade e wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e, Й“e wi'i: \"Pellet, ko onon woni tooГұuЙ“e Й“en"
  21,65,"Refti Й“e uggini ko'e maЙ“Й“e Й—en [Й“e wi'i:] gomЙ—ii hiЙ—a anndi Й—i'i wonaa wowlayЙ—i"
  21,66,"O maaki: \"Enee, on reway gaanin Alla kon ko nafataa on hay e huunde hara lorrataa on kadi"
  21,67,Bis mo'on e kon ko rewoton gaanin Alla. Kaa on hakkiltaa
  21,68,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Sunnee mo, wallee reweteeЙ—i mo'on Й—in, si tawii ko on gollooЙ“e"
  21,69,"Men Daali: \"Ko an yo yiite, laato Й“uuЙ“ol e kisiyee e dow Ibraahiima"
  21,70,ЖҒe faandanii mo pewje Men waЙ—i Й“e pertube Й“en
  21,71,"Men danndi mo [Men danndi kadi] Luutu faade e ndin leydi ndi Men barkini e mu'un wonannde tageefooji Й—in"
  21,72,"Men Okki mo Ishaaqa e Yaaquuba ka Й“eydugol, kala maЙ“Й“e Men waЙ—i [Й“e] moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e"
  21,73,"Men waЙ—i Й“e AlmaamiiЙ“e hiЙ“e fewna e Yamiroore Amen Men Wahayini faade e maЙ“Й“e gollugol moЖҙЖҙi Й—in e Гұinnugol Julde nden e Okkugol Jakka on, Й“e laatinoke ko Й“e Reway Й“e Men"
  21,74,"E Luutu Men Okki mo Г‘eeГұal e Ganndal, Men danndi mo immorde e nden Saare nde [yimЙ“e mu'un] laatinoo no golla soЙ“uЙ—i Й—in, pellet, kamЙ“e Й“e laatinoke yimЙ“e bonЙ“e faasiqiiЙ“e"
  21,75,"Men naadi mo e nder Yurmeende Amen, pellet, kanko ko o jeyaaЙ—o e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“en"
  21,76,"E Nuuhu tuma nde o noddunoo ko adii, Men jaabinani mo kanko e Й“eynguure makko nden immorde e saЙ—teende mawnde nden"
  21,77,"Men walli mo immorde e Й“en yimЙ“e fennuЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en. Pellet, kamЙ“e Й“e laatino yimЙ“e bonЙ“e, Men yooli Й“e, Й“e fow maЙ“Й“e"
  21,78,E Daawuuda e Sulaymaana tuma nde Й“e Гұaawaynoo fii ngesa mban tuma nde bonnunoo e nder mabba dammi yimЙ“e Й“en Men woni seediiЙ“e Гұaawoore maЙ“Й“e nden
  21,79,"Men Faamini nde Sulaymaana [Гұaawoore nden] gooto-kala e maЙ“Й“e Men Okki Г‘eeГұel e Ganndal Men elti wonndude e Daawuuda pelle Й—en hiЙ—e subhinoo e colli Й—in kadi, Men laatike golluЙ“e"
  21,80,"Men Anndini [Daawuuda] moЖҙЖҙinngol mekeГұaaji fii mo'on, fii yo Й—i reenu on immorde e hare mo'on. Taw si onon ko on jarnooЙ“e"
  21,81,"[Men eltani] Sulaymaana henndu ndun ko ndu bippooru hindu doga e yamiroore makko, faade e ndin leydi ndi Men barki e mu'un. Men laatike AnnduЙ“e kala huunde"
  21,82,"No e Seytanuuji Й—in, Й—in Й—i no mutana mo, Й—i golla golle gaanin Й—um. Men laatanike Й—i ReenooЙ“e"
  21,83,"[JaЕӢto kadi fii] Ayyuuba tuma nde o noddunoo Joomi makko, [O maaki:] \"Min dey memii lam lorra kan, ko An woni ЖҒuroowo Yurmeede yurmtooЙ“e Й“en"
  21,84,"Men jaabinani mo Men hunci ko heЙ“i mo kon immorde e lorra, Men Okkiti mo Й“eynguure makko nden e yeru maЙ“Й“e wonndude e maЙ“Й“e kadi, Й—um ko Yurmeende immorde ka Amen e waaju wonannde rewooЙ“e Й“en"
  21,85,"[JaЕӢto kadi fii] Ismaa'iila e Idriisa e Jalkifli, Й“en fow ko e munГұЙ“e Й“en Й“e jeyaa"
  21,86,"Men naadi Й“e e nder Yurmeende Amen nden, pellet, kamЙ“e ko Й“e jeyaaЙ“e e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“en"
  21,87,"[JaЕӢto kadi fii] Jannuuni tuma nde o yahunoo ko o tikkuЙ—o o sikki wonnde Men Hattanaake e hoore makko, o noddi ka niЙ“e; \"Wonnde reweteeЙ—o alaa si wanaa An Senayee wonanii Ma, min dey mi laatike jeyaaЙ—o e tooГұuЙ“e Й“en"
  21,88,"Men jaabinani mo, Men danndi mo immorde e suno ngon, ko wano nii kadi Men danndirta gomЙ—inЙ“e Й“en"
  21,89,"[JaЕӢto kadi fii] fii Jakariyaa tuma nde o noddunoo Joomo makko, [o maaki:] Jooma, wata A Й—alam bajjo, ko An woni ЖҒurЙ—o MoЖҙЖҙude ronooЙ“e Й“en"
  21,90,"Men jaabinani mo, Men Okki mo Yahyaa, Men moЖҙЖҙinani mo sonnaajo makko on, pellet, kamЙ“e Й“e laatinoke hiЙ“e yaccoo e [gollugol] moЖҙЖҙi Й—in hiЙ“e nodda Men ka rerЙ—ere e kulol Й“e laatinoke yannkinaniiЙ“e Men"
  21,91,"[JaЕӢto kadi fii] oya [suddiiЙ—o] reenunooЙ—o farju makko on Men wutti e makko immorde e Fittaandu Amen, Men waЙ—i mo kanko e geЙ—aljo makko on Maande wonannde winndere nden"
  21,92,"Pellet, Й—ee mofte mo'on ko mofte goote, ko Min woni Joomi mo'on Rewee Lam"
  21,93,"ЖҒe taЖҙi fiyaake maЙ“Й“e on hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, Й“e fow ko faade ka Am Й“e ruttoytoo"
  21,94,"Kala golluЙ—o immorde e moЖҙЖҙuЙ—i Й—in hara kanko ko o gomЙ—inЙ—o, dullugol alaa fii golle makko Й—en, pellet, Menen Men winndanay mo"
  21,95,"No Harmani saare nde Men halki Й—um, wonnde kamЙ“e Й“e ruttataako [ton]"
  21,96,"Haa si udditoyaama Yaajuuja e Maajuuja, hara kamЙ“e immorde e kala naЙ—el hiЙ“e sortoo"
  21,97,"Fodoore Goongaare nden Й“adike, tawi kayre puttini giiЙ—e Й“en yedduЙ“e, [Й“e wi'a:] \"Eeyoo bone amen, gomЙ—ii men laatinoke e nder welsindaare immorde e Й—u'um, ko woni, men laatike tooГұuЙ“e"
  21,98,"Pellet, onon e ko rewoton kon gaanin Alla, ko on doccote Jahannama. Onon, ko on joloyayЙ“e e magge"
  21,99,Sinndo Й“ee laatinoke reweteeЙ“e Й“e jolataano e magge. ЖҒe fow maЙ“Й“e ko Й“e luttinteeЙ“e e nder magge
  21,100,"No woodani Й“e e nder magge haraango, kamЙ“e Й“e nanataa nder ton"
  21,101,"Pellet, Й“en Й“e moЖҙЖҙi Й—in adanii Й—um immorde ka Amen Й“en Й—on ko Й“e woЙ—Й—intinteeЙ“e gaayi magge"
  21,102,"ЖҒe nanoytaa wuuЙ—aango magge kamЙ“e hiЙ“e e nder ko wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e Й—in lokaa(wooЙ—a) kon, ko Й“e duumotooЙ“e"
  21,103,"SuninoytaaЙ“e Й—enЖҙere mawnde nden, Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en no jaЙ“Й“ooЙ“e [Й“e wi'a:] \"Ko ndee woni Г‘alaande mo'on, nden nde laatinoЙ—on hiЙ—on fodee"
  21,104,"Г‘alnde Men taggoyta kammu ngun wano taggugol Й—erol defte. Ko wano Men fuЙ—Й—ori non ka arannde tagu Men ruttirta ngu, [Й—um] ko Fodoore e dow Amen, pellet, Menen Men laatike gollooЙ“e"
  21,105,"GomЙ—ii Men winndiino ka Jabuura Й“aawo Alluwal Reenaangal ngal, pellet, leydi ndin ko jeyaaЙ“e Am moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“en ronoyta ndi"
  21,106,"Pellet,no e Й—um [ko jaЕӢtaa Й—oo] jottingol wonannde yimЙ“e rewooЙ“e Й“en"
  21,107,Men Nuliraali ma si wanaa Yurmeende wonannde winndire nden
  21,108,"Maaku: \"Anndu ko Wahayinaa e am, wonndema ReweteeЙ—o mon On ko O ReweteeЙ—o Gooto. Enee, hara onon ko on jebbiliiЙ“e?\". @Corrected"
  21,109,"Si tawii Й“e Й—urnike, maaku: \"Mi anndinii on e dow fotondiral, pellet, mi anndaa si no Й“adii maaЙ—um si no woЙ—Й—i kon ko fodaЙ—on"
  21,110,"Pellet, Kanko hiMo Anndi ko feeГұi kon e konngol ngol, hiMo Anndi kadi ko suuЙ—oton"
  21,111,"Mi anndaa non, belejo'o Й—um ko jarrabuyee mo'on, e dakamme haa e dummunne"
  21,112,"Maaku: \"Jooma, Г‘aawir Goonga kan ko Joomi amen Hinnorante On woni WallitorteeЙ—o On e dow kon ko sifotoЙ—on"